Safety at work
Part 1
This workshop aims to look at the workplace hazards 
we might experience in our company. We‚Äôll look, 
in particular, at the ergonomic hazards that can be 
caused by a poor workstation set-up, or manual handling. 

What words does Rishi use to talk about the objective of the training?
aims to

this presentation aims to...
This presentation aims to go over the company's 
recommendations for a better workstation set-up.

I'd like to concentrate on...
In this talk, I'd like to concentrate on how to avoid back injuries.

"This presentation aims to...", "I'd like to concentrate on..." 
What is the function of these two expressions?
to explain the purpose of the presentation

This talk aims to clarify how heavy load should be lifted properly.

In this talk, I'd like to concentrate on how to avoid back injuries.

What words does he use to introduce his first point?
Safety at work
