"Let me move on to" has a similar meaning to "secondly".

"To start with...", "let me move on to..." 
What is the function of these expressions?
to organise points in a presentation

Let me move on to the work conditions of our employees.

What words does Rishi use to link points?
"That brings me to the fact..." is used to link points.

that brings me to the point...
